## Common issues

| Symptom                                          | Likely cause                                                  | Fix                                                  |
|--------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| `401 Unauthorized` on first call                 | API key wrong or `.env` not loaded                            | Re-source `.env`; verify in platform                 |
| Search returns 0 docs after ingest               | `groupName` mismatch between ingest and search                | Confirm both use the schema in [ARCHITECTURE.md](ARCHITECTURE.md) |
| `409 Conflict` on re-ingest                      | Same `fileName` already in the group                          | Delete-then-add (recipe in `scaffolds/`)             |
| Model never calls `search_context`               | Tool description too vague                                    | Tighten the tool's `description` to name *when* to use it (sentence starts with "Use whenever…") |
| Retrieval too noisy                              | `similarity_threshold` too loose / `limit` too high           | Set threshold ≥ 0.5; cap `limit` at 5–8              |
| Latency spikes on bulk ingest                    | Sync ingest above 100 docs                                    | Switch this path to `addAsync` + polling             |
